org.rplgleparser.api.LFLD

Interface IHeaderSection

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HeaderSection

    public interface IHeaderSection
    Public interface of classes that implement the IBM QUSLFLD Header Section interface. Allows read only access to all the data type values.
    Author:
    Eric N. Wilson
